Maintainer: Nicolas Frerebeau
    <nicolas.frerebeau@u-bordeaux-montaigne.fr>
Description: A collection of simple functions for cleaning rectangular data. 
    This package allows to detect, count and replace values or delete 
    rows/columns according to a specific predicate. In addition, it provides 
    tools to check conditions and return informative error messages.
